NK014(pha)005:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho
NK014(pha)005:1: ga rdo rje'i phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK014(pha)005:2: // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rdo rje'i phreng ba zhes bya ba /
NK014(pha)005:3: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)005:4: khyab bdag ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK014(pha)005:5: gdul dka' 'dul phyir he ru ka dpal gyi //
NK014(pha)005:6: rnam rol lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dkyil 'khor lha'i //
NK014(pha)005:7: 'khor lor snang mdzad dpal ldan bla mar 'dud //
NK014(pha)005:8: gang gi go 'phang 'khor lo tshogs chen sar //
NK014(pha)005:9: skal ldan myur bder bgrod byed lam gyi mchog /
NK014(pha)005:10: rdo rje 'dzin dbang tshogs kyi gshegs shul nyid //
NK014(pha)005:11: dam pa'i gsung gi rjes 'brangs 'dir gsal te //
NK014(pha)005:12: grub pa'i 'bras bu ci dgar 'byung ba'i sgo //
NK014(pha)005:13: dbang dang sgrub pa'i phrin las la brten cing //
NK014(pha)005:14: de yang dkyil 'khor las dang 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)005:15: zab don rdo rje'i phreng ba rnam par spel //
NK014(pha)005:22: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK014(pha)005:23: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK014(pha)005:26: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)005:27: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK014(pha)005:28: ces gsungs pa ltar rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas
NK014(pha)005:29: 'khor 'das thams cad kyii 'byung gnas su gyur pa
NK014(pha)005:30: gzhi'i rgyud ces bya ba ste /
NK014(pha)005:31: gdul bya'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin can no //
NK014(pha)005:33: gzhi'i rgyud de glo bur gyi dri ma las bral
NK014(pha)005:34: bar byed pa thabs kyi rgyud ces bya ba lam
NK014(pha)005:35: gyi dngos pos bsdus pa'i yan lag can te /
NK014(pha)005:36: yan lag gi dngos po bcur gnas pa nyid las 'dir /
NK014(pha)005:37: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud kyi don //
NK014(pha)005:38: ji snyed bcu yi gzhi nyid las //
NK014(pha)005:39: skabs kyi dgos pa dkyil 'khor dbang //
NK014(pha)005:40: zhes pa'i dang po dkyil 'khor la'ang /
NK014(pha)005:41: skabs dgos thog ma man+dala la //
NK014(pha)005:42: rgyud las gzhi gnyis gcig gsungs pa //
NK014(pha)005:43: zhes dkyil 'khor bdun las 'dir lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK014(pha)005:45: sdom tshig sa thig sta gon dang //
NK014(pha)005:46: tshon gyis bri dang dbye bsnyen pa //
NK014(pha)005:47: rab tu gnas shing rgyas pas bsreg /
NK014(pha)005:48: 'jug pa gnyis dang yon tan bshad //
NK014(pha)005:52: mjug gi bya ba dang gsum du gnas pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:59: slob ma la'ang dbang bskur ba tsam gyi ched du yin na mos slob kyi tshul gyis /
NK014(pha)005:62: grangs kyi bsnyen pa gsum rab 'bring tha ma'i sgo
NK014(pha)005:63: nas gang 'grub tsam zhig sngon du 'gro ba gzhir
NK014(pha)005:64: byas nas / khyad par gyi ched du bsnyen pa kha gso ba la 'jug cing /
NK014(pha)005:65: tshogs sgrub kyi ched yin na ni lam nges rdzogs
NK014(pha)005:66: kyi tshul gyis phyag rgya spros bcas man chad la
NK014(pha)005:67: brtan pa thob par bya dgos pa nyid do //
NK014(pha)005:68: gnyis pa las kyi gzhi bzung ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:69: chu bo 'dus pa'i ded dpon la //
NK014(pha)005:70: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi bla mas /
NK014(pha)005:71: srog lus longs spyod rnam gsum gyis //
NK014(pha)005:72: gsang ba'i rgyud las gsungs pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)005:73: mnyes byed gzhi yangs slob bu'i mchog /
NK014(pha)005:74: ces pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi slob bu'am sgrub grogs dang bcas pa ste /
NK014(pha)005:75: gnas dus yo byad sogs phun sum tshogs pa'i cha rkyen thams cad bzang zhing tshogs par bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:76: gsum pa sa'i cho ga la /
NK014(pha)005:77: brtag bslang tshad dbang sbyang bsrung slob //
NK014(pha)005:78: yongs su bzung bas rdzogs pa yin //
NK014(pha)005:79: zhes brgyad du bshad pa las 'dir bdun gyi /
NK014(pha)005:80: dang po sa brtag pa la /
NK014(pha)005:82: ngan na sbyang spo bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:85: sa rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)005:87: gang du bya ba'i gzhi de'i nam mkha' phyag rgya lnga yi dbyibs lta bu dang /
NK014(pha)005:88: bar snang gi kha dog dwangs shing gsal la 'khor lo la sogs pa'i dbyibs 'dra ba la /
NK014(pha)005:89: sa gzhi shis pa'i lo rgyus dang ldan cing /
NK014(pha)005:90: kha dog ma 'dres la snum mdangs chags pa /
NK014(pha)005:92: phyogs kyi ri sgros bzang zhing /
NK014(pha)005:93: shar lhor gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse lta bu
NK014(pha)005:94: med pa sogs mtshams kyi dgra bzhi med pa ste
NK014(pha)005:95: / dang po nam mkha' bar snang sa //
NK014(pha)005:96: nam mkha' phyag rgya lnga dbyibs la //
NK014(pha)005:97: bar snang mdog dang dbyibs su shes //
NK014(pha)005:98: sa gzhi lo rgyus rnam gnyis kyis //
NK014(pha)005:99: bkra shis rnam gnyis ldan mi ldan //
NK014(pha)005:100: dbyibs mdog phyogs mtshams brgyad brtag bya //
NK014(pha)005:103: phyi'i skyon thad ka sog le lta bu la sogs pa med pa /
NK014(pha)005:105: 'og gzhi gter du brkos brtags te //
NK014(pha)005:106: zhes pa ltar brkos pa na gseg ma dang /
NK014(pha)005:112: srog chags la sogs pa med pa /
NK014(pha)005:113: phyi nang gnyis ka'i skyon nya gro d+ha lta bu la sogs pa med cing /
NK014(pha)005:114: bkra shis pa'i r+ts+wa dang me tog yod pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:115: kha dog bzang zhing snum bag che ba /
NK014(pha)005:116: rtsigs ma dang rgyus pa sogs nyung zhing /
NK014(pha)005:117: brkos pa'i khung bus de nyid kyis bkang ba na lhag par gyur pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:118: gnyis pa ngan na sbyang spo bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:119: de ltar brtags pas ngan na sa gzhan du spo ba'am /
NK014(pha)005:120: skyon sbyangs te dag par byas pa'i gnas su brtsam zhing /
NK014(pha)005:121: khyad par khro bo la ma mo 'du ba'i dur khrod shis pa yin te /
NK014(pha)005:122: shis pa min na spo ba'am sbyang //
NK014(pha)005:123: skyon dag spangs te dur khrod du //
NK014(pha)005:124: dngos grub khro bo bsgrub par bya //
NK014(pha)005:126: gnyis pa sa bslang ba la /
NK014(pha)005:127: snang ba las bslang ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:128: mi snang ba las bslang ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:130: brtags pas rung ba'i sa de rgyal po sogs gzhan
NK014(pha)005:131: dbang ba zhig na rin gzhal ba sogs kyi sgo
NK014(pha)005:132: nas bslangs la bdag dbang bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:135: sa'i lha mo 'khor bcas la bslang ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:137: brtags pa'i gzhi der ba byung dang /
NK014(pha)005:139: bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa'i man+dala ji tsam bzhengs
NK014(pha)005:140: par 'dod pa'i dkyil 'khor tshad dang mnyam par byas
NK014(pha)005:142: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgoms la mchod cing bstod
NK014(pha)005:143: nas 'dod don gsol te nam mkha' la 'degs pa'o
NK014(pha)005:145: sa lha'i man+dala dri dang ba byung gis byug par
NK014(pha)005:146: ga bur dang tsan+dana gyi thig le gru bzhi pa
NK014(pha)005:147: me tog gi tshom bu bcas pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:148: sa bdag gtso 'khor gyi mchod gtor gser skyems dang bcas pa bshams te /
NK014(pha)005:149: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las /
NK014(pha)005:152: rang nyid skad cig gis khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil
NK014(pha)005:153: ba ljang ser zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas sna
NK014(pha)005:155: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK014(pha)005:156: khro bo'i chas can yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur par bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:157: mchod gtor gser skyems dang bcas pa ram yam kham gis sbyang /
NK014(pha)005:158: +aahh+aum gis 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i phung por byin gyis rlob la /
NK014(pha)005:159: rang gi thugs ka nas l+aam yig ser po gcig
NK014(pha)005:160: chad pa man+dala gyi dbus su gnas pa las sa'i
NK014(pha)005:161: lha mo gser gyi mdog can zhi zhing 'dzum pa
NK014(pha)005:162: dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)005:163: g.yas gser gyi bum pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:164: g.yon mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK014(pha)005:165: phag gi khri la bzhugs shing 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i 'od zer 'phro bar bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:166: ye shes lngas dbang bskur nas /
NK014(pha)005:167: rnam snang bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK014(pha)005:168: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlob /
NK014(pha)005:169: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes pas snyan bsnan la /
NK014(pha)005:171: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK014(pha)005:172: tshur gshegs lha mo brtan ma che //
NK014(pha)005:173: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK014(pha)005:174: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK014(pha)005:175: e h+ye hi ba su d+h+aa r+ai ma h+aa k+aa
NK014(pha)005:176: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK014(pha)005:179: dzahmh'u bam hohs gnyis su med par bstim la /
NK014(pha)005:184: ming sngags la i dam ba lim sogs btags pas gtor ma phul la /
NK014(pha)005:185: sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'og phyogs skyong //
NK014(pha)005:186: sku gser phyag na gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK014(pha)005:187: 'ja' tshon 'od ldan phag chen khri la bzhugs //
NK014(pha)005:188: de la phyag 'tshal bsnyen bkur mchod par 'bul //
NK014(pha)005:191: zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas 'dod pa'i las stsol
NK014(pha)005:192: ba la dgyes pa'i mdangs phyungs te 'khod par bsam
NK014(pha)005:193: mo // de nas 'khor gyi sa bdag mchod pa ni /
NK014(pha)005:194: mchod gtor rnams sngar bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK014(pha)005:196: s+th+aa na pa ti k+she tra p+aa la sa pa ri w+aa ra e h+ye hi /
NK014(pha)005:198: a k+aa ro'i sngags kyis gtor ma phul la /
NK014(pha)005:200: ri rab chen po'i gnas dang gling bzhi dang //
NK014(pha)005:201: rgya mtsho'i 'jing gnas gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK014(pha)005:202: kun dag'i bdag po dbang byed chen po dang //
NK014(pha)005:203: kun tu sa yi lha mo brtan 'bar ma //
NK014(pha)005:204: sa bdag mthu chen 'khor gyi gnas rnams su //
NK014(pha)005:205: mchod sbyin gtor ma dam pa 'di bsngosa pas //
NK014(pha)005:206: so so 'khor bcas re ba skong gyur nas //
NK014(pha)005:207: bdag gi las 'di'i 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK014(pha)005:210: ya hi gats+tshasa rang gnas su btang la mchod gtor rnams gshegs /
NK014(pha)005:211: de nas lha mo dge ba'i dpang du gsol ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:212: lag g.yas pa'i mthe bos mathe'u chung bsnan pa tri sh+au la'i rgyas sa la lan gsum gtug cing /
NK014(pha)005:214: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK014(pha)005:215: spyod pa'i tshul dang khyad par dang //
NK014(pha)005:216: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK014(pha)005:217: lha mo khyod kyis dpang mdzod cig /
NK014(pha)005:220: lag gnyis khu tshur gyen bstan gyi mthe chung sbrel /
NK014(pha)005:221: mdzub mo rtse sprad pa 'degs pa'i rgyas /
NK014(pha)005:223: zhes pas lha mo nam mkha' la dpang du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:224: de nas badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzahs dpang po'i lha rnams nam mkha' gang bar spyan drangs /
NK014(pha)005:225: h+aum bzhis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi byin bsdus
NK014(pha)005:226: nas bdag la thim pas bdag gi lus 'od kyi
NK014(pha)005:227: gong bur gyur par bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:228: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK014(pha)005:229: zhes brjod pas rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje sku
NK014(pha)005:230: mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas rdo
NK014(pha)005:231: rje dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK014(pha)005:232: mi bzad pa'i khro bo 'bar ba'i sdang mig bgegs
NK014(pha)005:233: la blta ba'i rkang mthil dang snying gar h+aum las
NK014(pha)005:234: sna tshogs rdo rje me rab tu 'bar bar bsam
NK014(pha)005:235: zhing bden stobs brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK014(pha)005:236: sa yi phyogs 'dir rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gis
NK014(pha)005:237: sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i ye shes
NK014(pha)005:238: kyi 'bras bu thob par bya ba'i ched du sgyu
NK014(pha)005:239: 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi
NK014(pha)005:240: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs su gsol bas /
NK014(pha)005:241: gang su yang rung ba'i 'byung po gdug pa can
NK014(pha)005:242: g.yog dang 'khor du bcas pa thams cad 'dir ma
NK014(pha)005:243: gnas par gzhan du dengs shig /
NK014(pha)005:244: gal te mi 'gro na de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK014(pha)005:245: cad kyis thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes las
NK014(pha)005:246: byung ba'i khro bo'i ye shes kyi rdo rje me
NK014(pha)005:247: rab tu 'bar ba 'dis khyed rnams kyi mgo bo
NK014(pha)005:248: tshal pa brgyar 'gas par 'gyur ta re /
NK014(pha)005:252: yungs thun gyis brab pa khro bo'i sprin du spro zhing /
NK014(pha)005:253: sum+b+ha bzla bas rdo rje gsor ba dang dril bu
NK014(pha)005:254: 'khrol bzhin pas rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor te bgegs
NK014(pha)005:255: bskrad la / h+aum ring por brjod pas /
NK014(pha)005:256: khro bo rnams slar 'dus nas srung ba'i gur khang
NK014(pha)005:257: sna tshogs rdo rje me rab tu 'bar ba dang
NK014(pha)005:258: bcas pas phyogs mtshams thams cad khyab par bsam la
NK014(pha)005:259: / sa'i dbus su brjid bag dang bcas pas 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)005:260: sngar bzhin bcas pa'i lag g.yas tri sh+au la'i rgyas /
NK014(pha)005:261: ji ltar che mchog he ru kas //
NK014(pha)005:262: ru dra bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK014(pha)005:263: chos kyi rgyal srid dpung gtsugs pa //
NK014(pha)005:264: de bzhin du ni bdag gis kyang //
NK014(pha)005:265: rgyal bar byas te dkyil 'khor bri //
NK014(pha)005:266: sa yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:267: rat+na p+aa sham sid+d+hi ku ru sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)005:268: zhes brjod pas lha mo 'dzum pa'i dmangs kyis 'od du zhu nas sa gzhi la thim pas /
NK014(pha)005:269: sa gzhi rin po che'i rang bzhin ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gyur par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:270: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK014(pha)005:272: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad bstan pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:282: nyi shu rtsa lnga pa ste /
NK014(pha)005:283: re re la yang nang gses su gnyis gnyis kyis ston pa ni gnas khang yangs dog dang /
NK014(pha)005:285: gang la mos pa'i dbang gis 'dam kha can du gsungs pa ste /
NK014(pha)005:286: slob bu'i mos pa dang sbyar nas //
NK014(pha)005:287: legs rtsigs ngos 'jam snyoms par bya //
NK014(pha)005:288: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'og tu las dang bya bas sbyang ba'i skabs su dran par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:290: dpag tshad rgyang grags rim pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)005:291: zhes pas rgyang grags dang dpag tshad sogs nas ji
NK014(pha)005:292: srid mkha' khyab kyi bar du rnal 'byor pa'i blo
NK014(pha)005:293: khyad dang sbyar te gsungs so //
NK014(pha)005:294: bzhi pa sa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:295: zangs sam dmar po'i shing las phur bu rtse mo
NK014(pha)005:296: zla gam gyi gzugs su byas pa zhig snod 'brus
NK014(pha)005:297: bkab la sogs par btsugs te bzhag la /
NK014(pha)005:298: pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK014(pha)005:299: rang gi snying ga'i h+aum las pad+ma he ru ka dmar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK014(pha)005:300: dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang zhags pa /
NK014(pha)005:302: smad phur bu zla gam rab tu 'bar ba'i rtse
NK014(pha)005:303: mo can du phyungs pa bkod pa'i phur bu dang
NK014(pha)005:305: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs te gzi byin dang ldan par byas la /
NK014(pha)005:307: pad+ma dbang gi khro mchog chags pa'i sku //
NK014(pha)005:308: ma lus dbang du sdud pa'i las mdzad pa //
NK014(pha)005:309: 'dzam gling ye shes rin chen sa 'di dag /
NK014(pha)005:310: bdag gi byang chub grogs su 'gyur bar mdzod //
NK014(pha)005:311: pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya wa sham ma na ye h+aum /
NK014(pha)005:312: wa sham ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)005:313: zhes brjod bzhin par dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la btab pas /
NK014(pha)005:314: phur bu las byung ba'i 'od kyis sa gzhi thams
NK014(pha)005:315: cad khyab cing bdag gi dbang du gyur par bsam
NK014(pha)005:317: sdom ni las dang sbyin sreg dang //
NK014(pha)005:318: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin //
NK014(pha)005:320: dang po las dang bya bas sbyang ba la /
NK014(pha)005:322: gza' nyi ma rgyu ba'i ston zla tha chung la
NK014(pha)005:323: sogs pa'i zla ba gsum gsum la rim pa bzhin
NK014(pha)005:324: / shar lho nub byang du mgo blta zhing /
NK014(pha)005:325: lho la sogs par phyogs te nyal bas /
NK014(pha)005:326: de'i lto ba'i thad nas sa brko bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:327: tshad ni dkyil 'khor ji tsam bya ba'i rgya'am khru
NK014(pha)005:328: gang gru bzhi tsam pa sa'i skyon 'byin nus par
NK014(pha)005:331: sol ba la sogs pa'i skyon rnams bsal nas /
NK014(pha)005:332: sa'i phud kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod la /
NK014(pha)005:333: sa de nyid kyis bkang bas mtho na bzang /
NK014(pha)005:336: yang dong de khru gang tsam du brus nas 'thas par bcags la chus bkang ste /
NK014(pha)005:337: yi ge brgya pa bzla bzhin du gom pa lnga
NK014(pha)005:338: bcur phyin nas ldog ste bltas pas gang na rab
NK014(pha)005:341: de nyid g.yas su 'khyil na'ang bzang /
NK014(pha)005:342: de las ldog na ngan pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:343: de dag las bzang por mthong nas brkos pa'i khung
NK014(pha)005:344: bu de nyid du rdzas sum cus gang ba'i bum
NK014(pha)005:345: pa a las zla ba'i steng du tram las rin
NK014(pha)005:346: po che'i mchod sdong dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i gter du
NK014(pha)005:348: sngar gyi sa dang shis pa'i sa bzang po gzhan gyis kyang bkang la /
NK014(pha)005:349: spos chus btab nas 'thas par bcags pa'i stegs bu dpangs su khru gang dang /
NK014(pha)005:350: rgyar khru gang la sogs pa nas ji tsam 'dod pa'i bar brtsigs la ngos mnyam par bya ste /
NK014(pha)005:353: ba byung lnga dang bcas pa'i go ma yes khyab par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:354: gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:355: gong gi mtshan ma rnams shin tu ngan par mthong na gzhan du spo ba'am /
NK014(pha)005:356: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg tshul bzhin du byas pas bsal bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:357: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:358: mtshan ma ngan pa 'bring tsam du snang na /
NK014(pha)005:359: rang gi lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la
NK014(pha)005:360: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re'i steng du h+aum mthing
NK014(pha)005:361: ga re res mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las
NK014(pha)005:362: rdo rje rtse lnga pa h+aum gis mtshan par bsam
NK014(pha)005:363: la / badz+ra ha na ha na kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)005:364: ces brjod cing sa la lan gsum bsnun pas /
NK014(pha)005:365: rdo rje dang h+aum gi 'od kyis sa'i nyes skyon
NK014(pha)005:366: thams cad sbyangs nas ye shes rang snang gi gzhir
NK014(pha)005:368: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la /
NK014(pha)005:372: sa dang sar 'dzin pa'i 'khrul rtog thams cad stong
NK014(pha)005:373: nyid de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings su rnam par dag
NK014(pha)005:374: par bsam la / ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK014(pha)005:377: h+aum gi sgra ring por brjod pas /
NK014(pha)005:378: rang rig skad cig gis h+aum las rdo rje sngon
NK014(pha)005:379: po h+aum yig mthing nag 'bar bas mtshan par gyur
NK014(pha)005:380: / de las e yam ra sum kem ram b+h+r+aum rnams 'og tu chad /
NK014(pha)005:383: 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las 'byung lnga rim brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK014(pha)005:384: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la /
NK014(pha)005:386: ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK014(pha)005:387: dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'byung bar 'gyur ba bzhin du
NK014(pha)005:388: bkra lam gyis gsal bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:389: drug pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK014(pha)005:390: gnas khang legs par brgyan la /
NK014(pha)005:391: slob dpon rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs nas /
NK014(pha)005:392: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis mtha' bskor zhing shar sgo nas
NK014(pha)005:393: zhugs te dbus kyi gdan la shar du phyogs pas
NK014(pha)005:394: 'khod la / bskyed sngags kyis rang nyid skad cig
NK014(pha)005:395: gi gtso bo yab yum du bskyed nas dbang bskur
NK014(pha)005:396: 'khod la / byin gyis rlob / mkha' gsang brlabs
NK014(pha)005:397: nas mnyam par sbyor ba'i bya bas sras kyi lha
NK014(pha)005:398: tshogs sum cu spro ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:399: dbang mo bskyed pa rnams sgrub thabs ltar gzhan sras kyi cho gas gsal btab la /
NK014(pha)005:400: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyiis dkyil 'khor pa
NK014(pha)005:401: dang bcas pa'i dus gsum gyi mgon po sras dang
NK014(pha)005:402: bcas pa thams cad mkha' khyab tu sad par bsam
NK014(pha)005:403: zhing / ru lu ru lu h+aum gis snyan bsnan /
NK014(pha)005:405: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol sogs phyi nang gsang
NK014(pha)005:406: ba'i mchod pa rnams kyis mchod cing bstod par bya'o
NK014(pha)005:407: // de nas phyogs bzhir gnas pa'i slob ma bzhi /
NK014(pha)005:411: karma khros pa'i rgyal mo bzhir bskyed /
NK014(pha)005:418: las mkhan nam de rnams rang rang gis gtso bo
NK014(pha)005:419: la kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pa
NK014(pha)005:422: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK014(pha)005:423: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK014(pha)005:424: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi mchog /
NK014(pha)005:425: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:427: yon tan rin chen 'byung ba'i gtso //
NK014(pha)005:428: ma lus kun gyi re skong ba //
NK014(pha)005:429: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK014(pha)005:430: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:432: rang bzhin dag pas gos pa med //
NK014(pha)005:433: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pa brnyes //
NK014(pha)005:434: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK014(pha)005:435: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:437: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pas //
NK014(pha)005:438: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK014(pha)005:439: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK014(pha)005:440: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:441: thams cad kyis thun mong du /
NK014(pha)005:442: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK014(pha)005:443: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK014(pha)005:445: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:447: bzhi med na gcig gis kyang phyogs de dag tu song nas bya /
NK014(pha)005:448: de yang med na bsgoms pas kyang rung ngo //
NK014(pha)005:449: de nas slob dpon gyis rdor dril 'dzin cing 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis bltas te /
NK014(pha)005:450: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi //
NK014(pha)005:451: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)005:452: che ge mo sogs don gyi phyir //
NK014(pha)005:453: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyid pas //
NK014(pha)005:454: bdag cag rjes su bzung ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)005:455: sa 'di shis par byin rlabs par //
NK014(pha)005:456: bde bar gshegs pas mdzad du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:457: zhes nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad rjes su bskul la /
NK014(pha)005:458: h+aum bzhis byin bsdus nas rang la bstim /
NK014(pha)005:459: de nas snyems pa dang bcas pas langs te /
NK014(pha)005:460: 'gro ba rnams la snying rjes bltas nas /
NK014(pha)005:461: slar yang rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje 'jigs shing
NK014(pha)005:462: rngams pa mi bzad pa'i khro bo'i sprin spro ba'i
NK014(pha)005:463: skur gyur pa'i mig gnyis ma dang ta las nyi
NK014(pha)005:465: mig 'bras h+aum las bskal pa'i mer 'bar bas kun tu blta zhing /
NK014(pha)005:466: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK014(pha)005:467: dang thugs rdo rjer mi phyed pa'i nga rgyal dang
NK014(pha)005:469: nga ni sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag /
NK014(pha)005:471: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i las byed kyis //
NK014(pha)005:472: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhan du dengs //
NK014(pha)005:474: thugs ka'i h+aum las khro bo'i sprin mi bzad par spro zhing /
NK014(pha)005:475: rkang mthil gnyis su h+aum las 'bar ba'i rdo rje re res mtshan par bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:478: h+aum bzhi pa'i drag sngags sgrog pa dang bcas pas dbang ldan nas brtsams te /
NK014(pha)005:479: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis g.yas su bskor nas dkyil 'khor
NK014(pha)005:480: gyi gzhi cis kyang mi shigs pa rdo rje'i rang
NK014(pha)005:481: bzhin du brtan par byin gyis rlob bo //
NK014(pha)005:483: stong pa'i ngang las pad nyi la gnas pa'i h+aum las sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK014(pha)005:485: e ra pa ti ye dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes pa'i bar sgrub thabs ltar gyi rjes su /
NK014(pha)005:486: slar yang rang gi thugs ka nas khro bo bcu phyung ste /
NK014(pha)005:487: mdun du bkod pa'i phur bu rnams dang gnyis su med par gyur pa ni /
NK014(pha)005:488: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum /
NK014(pha)005:491: zhes brjod pas khro bo bcur gyur te nas /
NK014(pha)005:492: de nas khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba tho ba thogs pa sprul te /
NK014(pha)005:494: khro bcu so so'i sngags kyi mthar /
NK014(pha)005:495: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya nas 'bar ba srung ba'i
NK014(pha)005:496: 'khor los phyogs kun gtams te cis kyang mi shigs
NK014(pha)005:497: par bsam mo // zhes pa'i bar sgrub thabs ltar byas la /
NK014(pha)005:500: steng gi phur bu shar dang /
NK014(pha)005:501: 'og gi phur bu nub tu gdab cing rdo rje'i
NK014(pha)005:502: gar dang stangs stabs kyi rol pa ci rigs pa'ang
NK014(pha)005:503: bya'o // de ltar chos thams cad sems las logs su med la /
NK014(pha)005:504: sems kyang stong nyid nam mkha'i rang bzhin du gnas
NK014(pha)005:505: pas bar du bcad bya gcod byed thams cad dmigs
NK014(pha)005:506: su ma grub pa de kho na nyid kyi bsrung
NK014(pha)005:507: ba'o // sngar bshad pa'i sa'i cho ga phal cher
NK014(pha)005:508: dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa logs su byed pa dang
NK014(pha)005:509: ba'o // / brkos nas stegs bu bya dgos pa'i sar yin la /
NK014(pha)005:510: gzhan du na mi snang ba la bslang ba tsam sngon du 'gro bas dbang du bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:511: sngags rgya ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba rnams byas nas /
NK014(pha)005:512: sa byin gyis rlob pa'i las la 'jug cing /
NK014(pha)005:513: sngar drangs pa'i las rim gyi sdom tshig tu bsrung ba /
NK014(pha)005:515: bzung ba zhes pa'i rim pas gsungs kyang /
NK014(pha)005:516: 'og tu don 'chad pa'i tshe bsrung rlob gnyis go ldog cing /
NK014(pha)005:517: bzung ba sta gon gyi dkyus su bshad pa ltar bde bas 'dir yang de bzhin byas so //
NK014(pha)005:518: de dag gi nub dang po'i bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:519: bzhi pa sta gon nam lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga la /
NK014(pha)005:520: de yang las rim gyi rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa thig la gnyis kyi ye thig dang /
NK014(pha)005:521: bzhi pa tshon gyis bri ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:522: lnga pa rnam pa dgod pa'i dbye ba rnams ni
NK014(pha)005:523: lag len bde phyir 'og tu dngos gzhi'i skabs su
NK014(pha)005:524: 'chad cing / drug pa rnam rgyal dang las bum bsnyen pa /
NK014(pha)005:525: gnyis pa'i nang tshan las thig gdab pa /
NK014(pha)005:526: bdun pa rab gnas la gsum las /
NK014(pha)005:527: yan lag dang slob bur rab gnas rnams sa bcad
NK014(pha)005:528: gsum pa sta gon gyi khongs 'dir blangs te lag
NK014(pha)005:529: len 'brel bsdebs nas gseb tshags su 'chad par bya'o
NK014(pha)005:532: yan lag can gyi rab gnas so //
NK014(pha)005:537: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gang du byung ba'i dbang ldan
NK014(pha)005:538: gyi phyogs su khru do pa'i man+dala dris byug la
NK014(pha)005:539: / sna tshogs pad+ma 'dab brgyad rdo rje'i ra ba dang bcas pa bri /
NK014(pha)005:540: de'i dbus su las bum chas ldan rdo rje rgya gram gyi mtshan ma can dgod /
NK014(pha)005:541: shar du ye shes dang las kyi thig skud /
NK014(pha)005:543: nub tu thod chu bdud rtsi lnga ldan /
NK014(pha)005:545: dbus dang mtshams kyi pad 'dab bzhi la rdul tshon
NK014(pha)005:546: lnga mdog rigs sdebs pa dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod
NK014(pha)005:547: pa dang / de dag gi mthar mchod gtor spyi dang mthun par bsham mo //
NK014(pha)005:549: sngon 'gro nas bzung bdag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa'i
NK014(pha)005:550: mthar thug pa sngon du 'gro bas las bum bsang
NK014(pha)005:551: sbyang / stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las byung ba'i
NK014(pha)005:552: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs
NK014(pha)005:553: su rdzogs pa'i nang du nyi ma'i gdan la h+aum
NK014(pha)005:554: las sna tshogs rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa yongs
NK014(pha)005:556: h+aum big+h+n+aam ta kri ta phata /
NK014(pha)005:558: khro bo'i mi 'chi thabs sbyor ljang nag rgya gram
NK014(pha)005:559: dang dril bu 'dzin pa'i skur gyur par bsam zhing
NK014(pha)005:560: / las rigs bdag por byas pa'i ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK014(pha)005:561: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlob /
NK014(pha)005:562: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK014(pha)005:564: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis med du bstim /
NK014(pha)005:565: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+rasa brtan par byas /
NK014(pha)005:569: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgyas las bum la reg ste /
NK014(pha)005:571: ces brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK014(pha)005:572: lha 'od du zhu nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor 'khyil bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)005:573: bum chu 'thor yab kyis blangs te /
NK014(pha)005:574: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he d+harma t+aa badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK014(pha)005:576: bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la gtor bas nyes skyon dag par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:577: de ni lhag gnas thams cad la bsang gtor bya ba'i don du'o //
NK014(pha)005:578: de nas thig gi lhag gnas ni /
NK014(pha)005:586: ye thig dang las thig gnyis ka'i skud rgyu zhing gi ba su ta'am /
NK014(pha)005:587: rgyus chen la bya bar gsungs na'ang /
NK014(pha)005:588: ye thig gi rgyur bya ba'am /
NK014(pha)005:589: yang na dam ye thun mong du ras bal la
NK014(pha)005:590: sogs pa dpa' bo'i rin gyis nyos pa la khyad
NK014(pha)005:591: par gyi rgyu cung zad re bsres pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:592: 'khal ba'i grogs ni gzhon nu ma mtshan ldan lo bcu drug lon pa la sogs pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:593: tshad srid du 'dzin pa'i cha ma gtogs pa dkyil 'khor las nyis 'gyur dang /
NK014(pha)005:594: sbom phra sgo'i nyi shu cha ste cha chung gi lnga cha'o //
NK014(pha)005:595: grangs ni ye shes kyi thig skud tshon sna lngas bsgyur ba lnga tshan lnga'am lnga tshan gcig dang /
NK014(pha)005:596: dam tshig gi thig skud dkar dmar sngo ste sum tshan gsum mam gsum tshan gcig go //
NK014(pha)005:599: spyod lam gsum ni 'og tu ston no //
NK014(pha)005:600: de nas rdo rje dang dril bu'i rab gnas ni /
NK014(pha)005:602: ces las bum gyi chus bsang /
NK014(pha)005:604: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i lte ba la dpal chen po /
NK014(pha)005:605: yar gyi rwa lnga la khrag 'thung rigs lnga /
NK014(pha)005:606: mar gyi rwa lnga la rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK014(pha)005:607: yas mas kyi pad+ma'i 'dab ma brgyad la gnas ma brgyad dang yul ma brgyad /
NK014(pha)005:608: dril bu'i lte ba dang pad+ma'i 'dab ma brgyad kyi phyogs bzhir rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK014(pha)005:609: mtshams bzhir gsang ba'i yum bzhi /
NK014(pha)005:610: zhal shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma dang /
NK014(pha)005:611: rtse mo'i rdo rje khrag 'thung rigs lnga rnams kyi skur gsal bar bskyed la /
NK014(pha)005:620: zhes brjod pas lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK014(pha)005:624: rdo rje thabs kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga'i ngo bo dang /
NK014(pha)005:625: dril bu shes rab kyi rang bzhin stong nyid chos kyi sgra dbyangs sgrog pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:626: gnyis ka'ang don dam pa'i byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du mos pa brtan par byas la /
NK014(pha)005:628: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK014(pha)005:629: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK014(pha)005:631: chos la de bzhin dbang sgyur shog /
NK014(pha)005:635: de nas thod chu'i rab gnas ni /
NK014(pha)005:637: stong pa'i ngang las dam rdzas kyi steng du h+aum
NK014(pha)005:638: ha he phata b+h+yo las khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil
NK014(pha)005:639: 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams cad gsal bar bskyed /
NK014(pha)005:647: ru lu cung zad bzlas la /
NK014(pha)005:648: h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od du zhu ba ye shes kyi bdud rtsir 'khyil bar bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:649: de nas tshon gyi lhag gnas ni /
NK014(pha)005:657: mtshon bya ye shes lnga mtshon byed rdul tshon du bstan pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:659: rab rin po che lnga'i phye ma dang /
NK014(pha)005:660: 'bring 'bru'i phye ma kha bsgyur ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:661: tha ma so phag la sogs pa'i phye ma tshon sna lngas kha dog bsgyur ba ste /
NK014(pha)005:662: gang ltar yang thal chen cung zad bsres pa'o //
NK014(pha)005:664: tshon sna lnga so so la /
NK014(pha)005:666: lnga tshan gcig gis kyang ngo //
NK014(pha)005:668: skabs 'dir thig tshon thun mong du bya ste /
NK014(pha)005:670: stong pa'i ngang las ye shes kyi thig skud dang
NK014(pha)005:671: tshon sna lnga so so'i steng du nyi zla la
NK014(pha)005:672: gnas pa'i h+aum zung lnga dang /
NK014(pha)005:673: dam tshig gi thig skud kyi steng du nyi zla la gnas pa'i h+aum zung gsum gsal bar gyur /
NK014(pha)005:676: 'phros 'dus so so'i phyag mtshan sa bon gyis mtshan pa rnams yongs su gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)005:677: khrag 'thung rigs lnga dang rigs gsum rang rang gi yum dang bcas pa'i skur gyur /
NK014(pha)005:686: zhes brjod pas lha rnams 'od du zhu nas thig tshon so so la thim par bsam /
NK014(pha)005:687: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK014(pha)005:688: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar
NK014(pha)005:689: spyan drangs la / rdo rje gsor bzhin du /
NK014(pha)005:690: hoh mi gnas ye shes chen po'i bdag /
NK014(pha)005:691: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs //
NK014(pha)005:692: thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)005:693: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gis ni //
NK014(pha)005:694: 'jigs byed chen po he ru ka'i //
NK014(pha)005:696: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK014(pha)005:697: bdag la mthu dang byin rlabs stsol //
NK014(pha)005:698: bdag la rdo rje ye shes kyis //
NK014(pha)005:699: thig tshon dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK014(pha)005:701: rang gi mig gnyis dzahyiga las skyes pa'i nyi zlar bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:702: dip+ta drish+ta gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na dzahdzah zhes brjod cing
NK014(pha)005:703: rdzi ma bskyod pa 'bar ba'i lta stangs kyis bskul
NK014(pha)005:704: bas nam mkha'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams sbyor ba
NK014(pha)005:706: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs ye shes lnga'i sngags
NK014(pha)005:707: rnams brjod pas de rnams brjod pas de rnams kyi
NK014(pha)005:708: thugs ka nas ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyi 'od
NK014(pha)005:710: ye shes kyi thig skud dang tshon so so la
NK014(pha)005:711: thim pas de nyid ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gyur
NK014(pha)005:712: par bsam zhing / 'bru lnga brjod bzhin par slob
NK014(pha)005:713: ma dang bcas pas dang por srad bu lnga tshan
NK014(pha)005:715: de nas lnga po yang gcig tu bsgril la brdogs nas gser la sogs pa'i snod du bzhag /
NK014(pha)005:716: de bzhin du k+aa ya badz+ra sogs sku gsung thugs
NK014(pha)005:717: kyi sngags gsum brjod pas nam mkha'i de bzhin gshegs
NK014(pha)005:718: pa rnams kyi gnas gsum nas rdo rje gsum gyi
NK014(pha)005:719: rang bzhin gyi 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum byung
NK014(pha)005:720: / dam tshig gi thig skud so so la thim
NK014(pha)005:721: pas de nyid sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor gyur
NK014(pha)005:722: / par bsam zhing / 'bru gsum brjod bzhin du gsum tshan re re so sor sgril /
NK014(pha)005:723: de nas gsum po'ang gcig tu sgril nas sngar bzhin bzhag /
NK014(pha)005:725: +aahsarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK014(pha)005:726: zhes bzlas pas rin po che'i rdul phra rab kyi rdul tshon 'bar bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)005:727: bris pa'i yig 'bru rnams kyang mi mngon par spungs shing bsnun par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:729: nyes spong ni 'og tu ston no //
NK014(pha)005:730: gnyis pa yan lag can gyi rab gnas la /
NK014(pha)005:733: lha lhag par gnas pa dang gsum las /
NK014(pha)005:734: dang po bum pa rab gnas la /
NK014(pha)005:738: rgyas par na mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bum pa lha grangs dang mnyam pa'am /
NK014(pha)005:739: bsdu na rigs lngar bsdus te lha bum lnga /
NK014(pha)005:740: shin tu bsdu na rnam rgyal dang /
NK014(pha)005:742: rnam rgyal ni dbus kyi khro bo gsang bum kho nar bsdus kyang rung ngo //
NK014(pha)005:744: pho mo'i thod pa mtshan ldan gyi nang du chang
NK014(pha)005:745: dang rdzas sum cu'i bcud kyis bkang ba dar mthing
NK014(pha)005:746: dmar gyis bcings shing lcang los brgyan pa ste /
NK014(pha)005:757: a pa ra tsi ste sman lnga /
NK014(pha)005:758: gser dngul mu tig byu ru mu men te rin po che lnga /
NK014(pha)005:759: nas 'bras gro til sran ma ste 'bru lnga /
NK014(pha)005:760: gur gum gla rtsi dza ti tsan+dana dkar dmar te dri lnga /
NK014(pha)005:761: de ltar lnga tshan lnga po'i steng du bdud rtsi lnga bsnan pas sum cu'o //
NK014(pha)005:762: de yang bum pa lha grangs dang mnyam pa la
NK014(pha)005:763: ni gang du bzhag pa'i gnas dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK014(pha)005:765: bum pa lnga pa'i tshe na dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK014(pha)005:766: kyi lte ba dang phyogs bzhi ste gtso bo rigs
NK014(pha)005:767: lnga'i gnas su ma 'chol bar bzhag /
NK014(pha)005:768: bum pa gcig las med na gtso bo'i gnas su dgod /
NK014(pha)005:769: mtha' mchod pa rnams kyi ji ltar mdzes par bskor /
NK014(pha)005:770: las bum sgo'i nang rol gyi g.yas sam rang gi
NK014(pha)005:771: mdun sogs gang bder bsang gtor gyi don du bzhag
NK014(pha)005:773: bum pa rnams las thams cad pas bsang /
NK014(pha)005:774: sh+au nya t+aas stong par sbyang /
NK014(pha)005:775: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las byung ba'i bum pa
NK014(pha)005:776: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang du
NK014(pha)005:777: ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK014(pha)005:778: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa gsal bar bsam
NK014(pha)005:779: la / bum pa lha grangs dang mnyam pa yod
NK014(pha)005:780: na so so'i gdan la lha de dang de bskyed
NK014(pha)005:781: la / cing / bum pa lnga pa'i tshe bla ma gong ma dag gis /
NK014(pha)005:782: dbus su dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo tshang ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:784: shar dang shar lho'i gnas ma dang yul ma /
NK014(pha)005:786: shar gyi dbang mo bdun rnams bsdus pa sogs rigs so sor phye mod kyang /
NK014(pha)005:787: khyab bya dkyil 'khor tshang ba khyab byed rdo rje'i rigs gcig tu bsdus rjes /
NK014(pha)005:788: slar yang khyab byed dang khyab bya gzhan bzhi po
NK014(pha)005:789: so sor phye ba la dgos pa lhag po ma
NK014(pha)005:790: mthong bas / 'dir rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang bstun te /
NK014(pha)005:791: dbus su badz+ra he ru ka la dbang phyug ma'i gtso mo bzhi dang sgo ma bzhi /
NK014(pha)005:792: rigs gzhan bzhi la rang rang gi phyogs dang mtshams kyi gnas yul dang /
NK014(pha)005:794: dbang mo lnga lnga re bsdus pa skyon gyi dgag cha chung bar mngon no //
NK014(pha)005:795: bum pa gnyis pa'i tshe rnam rgyal bum pa'i nang
NK014(pha)005:796: du rang rang gi gdan la h+aum zung lnga dang
NK014(pha)005:800: b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams gnas par gyur /
NK014(pha)005:803: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las so so'i phyag mtshan sa bon gyis mtshan pa rnams su gyur /
NK014(pha)005:806: slar yang 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK014(pha)005:807: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka zhes sogs so so'i bskyed sngags rnams rim bzhin brjod pas /
NK014(pha)005:808: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po badz+ra he ru
NK014(pha)005:809: ka la sogs te lnga bcu rtsa brgyad khrag 'thung
NK014(pha)005:810: rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo thams cad yongs
NK014(pha)005:811: su rdzogs par gsal bar bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:820: bdag gi zhal nas sngags kyi phreng ba byung /
NK014(pha)005:821: gzungs thag la 'khril te song bas bum pa'i lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK014(pha)005:822: snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang sems ye shes kyi bdud rtsir babs pas bum pa gang bar bsam zhing /
NK014(pha)005:823: lha so so'i rtsa sngags gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar ba ci nus su bzlas pa'i mthar /
NK014(pha)005:824: tap+de tap+de ma h+aa tap+de s+w+aa h+aa /
NK014(pha)005:825: zhes thod chu bum nang du phul bas /
NK014(pha)005:826: lha thams cad chags pa chen pos ye shes kyi
NK014(pha)005:827: bdud rtsir zhu ba bum chu dang ro gcig tu
NK014(pha)005:829: bdug spos kyis bdug par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:830: slob mar dbang bskur ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:833: sgrub pa dngos grub kyi dbang len pa rnams la bum pa nges par 'cha' dgos mod /
NK014(pha)005:834: sgrub mchod tsam la nges par dgos pa ma yin kyang 'grub na ni legs so //
NK014(pha)005:835: gnyis pa slob ma lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga ni /
NK014(pha)005:836: dbang chog tu shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:837: gsum pa lha lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga ni /
NK014(pha)005:838: sa bzung ba'i sa khongs smos pa nyid de /
NK014(pha)005:839: de la thig gdab pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:842: lhag gnas byas pa'i bum pa rnams dben par bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK014(pha)005:845: ces las bum gyi chus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la
NK014(pha)005:846: bsang gtor byas nas bdud rtsi dang bcas pa'i dris
NK014(pha)005:847: byug cing 'bri bar 'gyur ba'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha'
NK014(pha)005:848: la gsal bar dmigs te dam tshig gi thig skud
NK014(pha)005:849: dri zhim po'i thig chal las phyungs pa cho ga
NK014(pha)005:850: bzhin du gtong len byas la /
NK014(pha)005:851: dang po shar nub tshangs thig gdab //
NK014(pha)005:852: dbus nas phyogs bzhir mtshan ma bya //
NK014(pha)005:853: shar nub tshad nas gnyis pa dang //
NK014(pha)005:854: phyogs bzhi'i tshad nas zur thig btsal //
NK014(pha)005:855: tshangs pa'i thig gi phyogs bzhi ru //
NK014(pha)005:856: cha chen dgu dgu bco brgyad gdab //
NK014(pha)005:857: de nas cha chen nang ma gsum //
NK014(pha)005:858: phyed du gtubs te drug tu byas //
NK014(pha)005:859: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma phyed //
NK014(pha)005:860: gnyis pa dang ni bzhi pa'i nang //
NK014(pha)005:861: bzhi cha gcig re gdab par bya //
NK014(pha)005:862: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis bsil //
NK014(pha)005:863: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK014(pha)005:864: de ni nang gi sgo yin no //
NK014(pha)005:865: cha chen bzhi pa phyi yi khyams //
NK014(pha)005:866: lnga dgu dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK014(pha)005:867: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK014(pha)005:868: bdun pa brgyad pa cha bzhir bgo //
NK014(pha)005:869: phyi sgo tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du //
NK014(pha)005:870: cha chen gnyis gnyis btab pa las //
NK014(pha)005:871: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma bcad //
NK014(pha)005:872: gnyis pa cha phran bzhi ru bsil //
NK014(pha)005:873: dbus nas zlum bskor cha phran lnga //
NK014(pha)005:874: gcig dang lnga dang gcig rnams ni //
NK014(pha)005:875: lte ba mu khyud rtsibs rtsibs brten //
NK014(pha)005:876: de nas nang gi glo 'bur gyi //
NK014(pha)005:877: dkyus su sgo tshad zheng cha phran //
NK014(pha)005:878: khyams rtsig 'dod snam pha gu dang //
NK014(pha)005:879: d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab ste //
NK014(pha)005:880: sgo khyud sgo tshad 'gram logs gnyis //
NK014(pha)005:881: de yi phyed yin nang sgo'o //
NK014(pha)005:882: phyi ma rim bzhin phyi khyams rtsig /
NK014(pha)005:883: 'dod snam pha gu d+r+wa phyed dang //
NK014(pha)005:884: shar bu mda' yab rnams kyi sa //
NK014(pha)005:886: de yi phyed yin mun pa dang //
NK014(pha)005:887: ka ba ka rgyan cha phran re //
NK014(pha)005:888: rta babs brgyad po cha mnyam las //
NK014(pha)005:889: dang po ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam //
NK014(pha)005:890: gnyis gsum de nas gcig phyir bskyed //
NK014(pha)005:891: bzhi pa gnyis bskum lnga pa gcig /
NK014(pha)005:892: phyir 'phyar drug pa gnyis su bskum //
NK014(pha)005:893: bdun brgyad rim bzhin re re 'phyar //
NK014(pha)005:894: rim par rta rkang chu skyes dang //
NK014(pha)005:895: sgrom dang za ra tshags sna 'phyong //
NK014(pha)005:897: snam bu gsum pa'i phyi thig dang //
NK014(pha)005:898: tshangs thig 'dzom sa nas bzung ste //
NK014(pha)005:899: cha phran gnyis kyis glang rgyab dbus //
NK014(pha)005:900: mun pa'i phyi thig tshangs gnas kyi //
NK014(pha)005:901: g.yas g.yon cha phran gnyis 'das nas //
NK014(pha)005:902: sngar bzhin bskor ba mun pa'i mthongs //
NK014(pha)005:903: mu ran cha phran gcig gis bskor //
NK014(pha)005:905: gdugs ni cha phran re re'o //
NK014(pha)005:906: mda' thig zur nas cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)005:907: dor mthar cha phran gcig dang gnyis //
NK014(pha)005:908: cha chen gcig dang de phyed dang //
NK014(pha)005:909: cha chen gcig tu bskor ba ni //
NK014(pha)005:910: rtsibs rten pad+ma dur khrod dang //
NK014(pha)005:911: rdo ra me ri rnams kyi sa //
NK014(pha)005:912: rtsa thig sgo khyud 'dzom rtse nas //
NK014(pha)005:913: rtsibs rten tshangs thig 'dzom pa'i bar //
NK014(pha)005:914: g.yas nas gcig shos g.yon nas g.yas //
NK014(pha)005:918: spyod lam ni ye thig gi skabs bzhin 'dir yang shes par bya ba nyid do //
NK014(pha)005:919: skabs 'dir skya thig tsam btab nas /
NK014(pha)005:920: dam ye'i thig 'debs tshul sbrel nas 'og tu gsungs pa'ang don la gnas pa yin mod kyi /
NK014(pha)005:921: 'on kyang bya sla ba'i ched du las thig 'dir
NK014(pha)005:922: btab nas skya thig mi dgos par byas pa yin
NK014(pha)005:923: no // gzhan du kha cig las thig ma btab
NK014(pha)005:924: par sta gon gyi lha gnas nges pa mi rtogs
NK014(pha)005:925: pa'i phyir 'dir nges par 'debs dgos zhes smra na'ang
NK014(pha)005:926: mtha' gcig tu nges par ma mthong ngo //
NK014(pha)005:928: thig gi man+dala de'i mthar lha grangs sogs ci 'byor ba'i mchod pa bshams la /
NK014(pha)005:929: dkyil 'khor gyi gnas su rang nyid gtso bo yab
NK014(pha)005:930: yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i sems sprin las b+h+r+aum 'phros
NK014(pha)005:931: te gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su
NK014(pha)005:933: lha gnas so sor rang rang gi rtsa sngags la
NK014(pha)005:934: ma ni pad+ma ye s+w+aa h+aa btags pa'i sngags brjod
NK014(pha)005:935: cing byang sems dkar dmar tsan+dana dang sbyar ba'i thig
NK014(pha)005:936: le gtso bo'i gnas su gru bzhi pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:937: gzhan rnams su zlum por byas la /
NK014(pha)005:938: me tog gi tshom bu bkod nas /
NK014(pha)005:940: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su nyi zla'i gdan la 'dug par mos la /
NK014(pha)005:941: gtso bo yab yum gyi skur gsal btab pa la dbang bskur byin gyis rlob /
NK014(pha)005:942: mkha' gsang byin brlabs dang ldan pa'i sgo nas snyoms
NK014(pha)005:943: par zhugs pa'i byang chub kyi sems sprin sku'i dbyibs
NK014(pha)005:944: brgyud rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi pad+mora spros pa
NK014(pha)005:945: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK014(pha)005:946: gyi 'khor lor rdzogs pa rnams rang rang gi gnas
NK014(pha)005:947: ji lta bar bzhugs par bsam la /
NK014(pha)005:948: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK014(pha)005:955: spos dang bcas pa'i rdor dril 'dzin bzhin pas //
NK014(pha)005:957: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK014(pha)005:958: mgon po dam can ji snyed pa //
NK014(pha)005:959: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK014(pha)005:960: sras bcas thabs cig gshegs nas kyang //
NK014(pha)005:961: sa gzhi yongs su bzung bar mdzod //
NK014(pha)005:962: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)005:963: zhes gsol ba btab pas lha thams cad dgyes par
NK014(pha)005:964: rol pa'i gzi byin mtha' yas pas de nyid du
NK014(pha)005:965: thim pas thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du
NK014(pha)005:966: gsal bar bsam pa de dag ni lhag gnas kyi
NK014(pha)005:967: cho ga ste nub gnyis pa'i bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:968: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i cho ga la /
NK014(pha)005:977: tshon gyis bri ba gnyis las /
NK014(pha)005:979: nangs par be g+aa kra ma yam /
NK014(pha)005:980: zhes 'degs pa'i rgyas sta gon gyi lha nam mkhar btegs la /
NK014(pha)005:981: tshom bu rnams gzhan du bsal /
NK014(pha)005:982: sngar rab gnas byas pa'i ye shes kyi thig skud
NK014(pha)005:983: de nyid slob dpon bdag po'i nga rgyal gyis nub
NK014(pha)005:984: nas shar dang / thig g.yog yum du mos pa
NK014(pha)005:985: shar nas nub tu phyogs pa la g.yon pa'i khu
NK014(pha)005:986: tshur gyis lte bar bzung nas /
NK014(pha)005:987: dzahdzahdzah zhes brjod pas thig skud kyi rtse mo nas g.yas pas bzung ba thig g.yog la gtod cing /
NK014(pha)005:988: des kyang de skad brjod cing drangs la shar nub kyi tshangs thig dang po dang /
NK014(pha)005:989: lhor gnas te byang du blta bas tshangs thig gnyis pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:990: mer gnas te rlung du blta bas zur thig dang po dang /
NK014(pha)005:991: bden bral nas dbang ldan du blta bas zur thig gnyis pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:992: mer gnas te byang du blta bas shar gyi rtsa thig dang /
NK014(pha)005:993: rlung nas lhor blta bas nub kyi dang /
NK014(pha)005:994: slar yang rlung nas shar du blta bas byang gi dang /
NK014(pha)005:995: yang me nas nub tu blta bas lho'i rtsa thig ste /
NK014(pha)005:996: thig chen brgyad po las thig gi steng gi nam
NK014(pha)005:997: mkha' la mtheb mdzub gnyis kyis se gol gyi sgra
NK014(pha)005:1000: badz+ra s+au tra sa ma ya ma ti kra ma h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)005:1001: ces brjod pas mkha' khyab kyi rgyal ba rnams sad
NK014(pha)005:1002: cing ye shes kyi thig dam tshig gi thig la
NK014(pha)005:1003: ro mnyam du gyur par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:1004: thig skud sngar gyi snod du bzhag pa /
NK014(pha)005:1008: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK014(pha)005:1009: badz+ra muh zhes pas thig skud kyi ye shes pa nam mkha'i lha'i thugs kar gshegs /
NK014(pha)005:1010: ye thig thebs nas de la 'gom dgos pa byung na h+r+aihzhesa sgra ring po dang /
NK014(pha)005:1011: 'degs pa'i rgyas nam mkhar btegs pa'i 'og nas 'dzul bar mos shing /
NK014(pha)005:1012: sgo thad kyi rtsa thig phyis la /
NK014(pha)005:1013: slar yang phab la bstim mo //
NK014(pha)005:1015: skud pa chad na slob dpon 'chi //
NK014(pha)005:1016: thig sna shor na slob bu 'chi //
NK014(pha)005:1017: phyogs 'khrul bas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK014(pha)005:1018: rgyun chad lam la gnod par 'gyur //
NK014(pha)005:1019: de phyir mkhas ldan sgrims te bya //
NK014(pha)005:1020: zhes bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:1021: gnyis pa tshon gyis bri ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:1022: dbang phyug rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs te /
NK014(pha)005:1023: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su phur pa dngos su btab pa yin na /
NK014(pha)005:1024: tshon sna lnga 'byung rigs bsdebs pas m+aum t+aam sogs
NK014(pha)005:1025: rim par brjod cing khung bu mnyam par bkang la
NK014(pha)005:1027: slar yang g.yas pa'i mtheb srin gyis tshon rtsi lnga
NK014(pha)005:1028: cung zad blangs pa g.yon pa'i mthil du bzhag la
NK014(pha)005:1029: / +aahsarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK014(pha)005:1031: g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga la nyi ma'i steng du yab kyi 'bru lnga /
NK014(pha)005:1032: g.yon pa'i sor mo lnga la zla ba'i steng du yum gyi 'bru lnga gnas par bsam ste /
NK014(pha)005:1033: g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga tshoms kyis g.yon pa'i tshon rtsi khung bu'i steng du bkod la /
NK014(pha)005:1034: don ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin rtags keng
NK014(pha)005:1035: rus chen po'i ri rab tu gyur par bsam mo
NK014(pha)005:1036: // de nas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su gnas pas
NK014(pha)005:1037: g.yon pa'i khu tshur gyis dbang ldan nas brtsams te
NK014(pha)005:1038: rtsig pa lnga phyi nas ljang dmar ser dkar sngo
NK014(pha)005:1039: ba rnams zheng thig skud gang dang dpangs mathe'u chung
NK014(pha)005:1040: phyed tsam pa ma 'dres shing snyoms pa sgo tshad
NK014(pha)005:1041: gcig gi tshad tsam du bris te ka p+aa las
NK014(pha)005:1043: rtsig pa sbrel ran pa na kha phye la pra brtag ste /
NK014(pha)005:1044: ku ku r+aa dzas mnyam sbyor dkyil chog tu /
NK014(pha)005:1045: re kh+aa dma' bas mi 'grub cing //
NK014(pha)005:1046: g.yon pos gdung ba bskyed par byed //
NK014(pha)005:1047: chad pas slob dpon slob ma dag /
NK014(pha)005:1049: chad lhag las ni nad 'byung zhing //
NK014(pha)005:1051: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par bya zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1053: de kho na nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis skyon thams cad sel ba yin no //
NK014(pha)005:1054: slob dpon gyis rdzogs par bri mi nus na /
NK014(pha)005:1055: slob ma rnams kyis kyang lag pa byin brlabs sngar bzhin byas nas bri bar bya ste /
NK014(pha)005:1056: de la dbus kyi lte ba mthing ga /
NK014(pha)005:1057: mu chad dang gru chad ljang gu /
NK014(pha)005:1060: rtsibs rten sngon po la rdo rje'i phreng ba /
NK014(pha)005:1063: khyams nang ma ser po dang phyi ma khrag khyams /
NK014(pha)005:1064: rtsig pa nang ma nang nas sngo dmar dkar po dang /
NK014(pha)005:1065: phyi ma nang nas mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba /
NK014(pha)005:1067: pha gu ser po thod pas dkrigs pa /
NK014(pha)005:1068: d+r+wa ba'i gzhi nag po la sbrul dang thod phreng gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK014(pha)005:1069: gzhi sngon po la rkang lag gi shar bu /
NK014(pha)005:1070: mda' yab dkar po mchod rten ris /
NK014(pha)005:1071: mun pa dang glang rgyab nag po /
NK014(pha)005:1073: rta babs snam bu brgyad ni /
NK014(pha)005:1074: rta rkang gzhi sngon po la rdo rje 'greng bu ser po /
NK014(pha)005:1075: chu skyes dmar po sgrom mdzes tshon /
NK014(pha)005:1076: zar tshags dkar po la gzhi nag po /
NK014(pha)005:1078: sgril 'phyang gzhi nag po la d+r+wa ba dkar po /
NK014(pha)005:1079: shar bu dkar po gzhi sngon po la sgrigs pa /
NK014(pha)005:1080: rgya phubs khyung mgo mthing ga /
NK014(pha)005:1082: 'khor lo dang ri dwags ser po /
NK014(pha)005:1088: dur khrod kyi gzhi nag po la chos rnams kyis 'jigs par brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)005:1089: rdo ra gzhi mthing ga la rdo rje dkar po'am ser po /
NK014(pha)005:1090: me ri sna tshogs sam dmar ser /
NK014(pha)005:1091: rta babs dang mda' yab kyi khor yug la zhing gi rgyal mtshan dang /
NK014(pha)005:1093: sgo'i phyi rol du skyes bu gsal shing gi phug pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1095: rak+ta'i rdzing bu rnams phyogs rer gnyis gnyis spel mar bris la /
NK014(pha)005:1096: tshon gyis bri ba'i las rnams rdzogs pa'i mthar /
NK014(pha)005:1100: bzhi bsnol sogs kyis mchod nas /
NK014(pha)005:1101: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa nam mkha'i lha'i thugs kar gshegs nas dman pa rnams dben par bzhag go //
NK014(pha)005:1103: bag med gyur pa'i nyes pa yang //
NK014(pha)005:1104: bshad pa'i rjes su shes par bya //
NK014(pha)005:1105: zhes pas thig gi skabs su bshad pas mtshon cing /
NK014(pha)005:1107: de sel ba'i gnyen po yang sngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK014(pha)005:1108: gnyis pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK014(pha)005:1109: rin po che'am lde gu sogs las byas pa'i lha
NK014(pha)005:1110: so so'i sku brnyan yod na de dang de'i gnas
NK014(pha)005:1112: med na tshon gyis bri ba'i rjes 'brel nyid du sku gzugs sam /
NK014(pha)005:1115: rang mdog dang mtshungs pa'i thig le'i rnam pa can gyi bar ci nus su bri zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1116: de yang gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK014(pha)005:1117: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK014(pha)005:1118: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK014(pha)005:1119: zhes rim pa tha dad du bri tshul yang bshad do //
NK014(pha)005:1120: gsum pa rab gnas bya ba la gsum las /
NK014(pha)005:1121: dang po bum pa'i rab gnas dang /
NK014(pha)005:1122: gnyis pa slob ma rab gnas gnyis gong du song //
NK014(pha)005:1123: gsum pa dkyil 'khor rab gnas la /
NK014(pha)005:1127: sngar lhag gnas byas pa'i bum pa rnams spos dang
NK014(pha)005:1128: rol mos sna drangs te dkyil 'khor la g.yas su
NK014(pha)005:1129: bskor nas lha so so'i gnas rnams su many+dzi la
NK014(pha)005:1130: sogs pa'i stegs la dgod cing /
NK014(pha)005:1131: bum pa lnga'am gcig tu bsdus pa la ni gtso
NK014(pha)005:1132: bo lnga'i gnas sam dbus nyid du bzhugs su gsol
NK014(pha)005:1133: / las bum ni slob dpon gyi mdun du'o //
NK014(pha)005:1134: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor dri bzang gis byug cing /
NK014(pha)005:1135: me tog gi sil ma bkram /
NK014(pha)005:1136: phyogs kun tu bla re dang /
NK014(pha)005:1140: ba dan sna tshogs pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1141: gos zung du mas bkod legs su brgyan par bya zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1145: dri chab rnams lha grangs dang mnyam pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1146: gzhan yang zhabs bsil la sogs pa phyi'i mchod pa rnams dang /
NK014(pha)005:1147: sman gtor rak+ta la sogs pa nang gi mchod pa
NK014(pha)005:1148: rnams kyang ci 'byor bas phyi'i khor yug rnams mdzes
NK014(pha)005:1149: par bya ste / bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK014(pha)005:1150: rgyan phreng btung dang bro bas bskor //
NK014(pha)005:1152: skabs 'di dag tu bgegs bskrad cing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1153: dkyil 'khor bskyed nas lha bstim pa /
NK014(pha)005:1156: phyag len 'gar dkyil 'khor byin 'bebs kyang mdzad pa cho ga rgyas pa'i yan lag tu 'byung na'ang /
NK014(pha)005:1157: rtsa ba'i rtsis 'gos ma bsdus pas chad pa'i dgag
NK014(pha)005:1158: cha chung zhing 'jug pa bde ba'i dbang du byas
NK014(pha)005:1160: gnyis pa rab gnas dngos dang /
NK014(pha)005:1162: 'dir rgyas pa'i las dang sbrel te gzhan du bshad pa bzhin bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:1163: lnga pa dkyil 'khor sgrub pa la /
NK014(pha)005:1166: mchod bstod sogs bya ba dang /
NK014(pha)005:1171: slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi shar ngos su phyogs pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1172: gzhan rnams kyang ji ltar 'os par 'dug nas /
NK014(pha)005:1173: thog mar rgyud sbyang ba nas bzung mchod rdzas byin gyis rlob pa'i bar sngon du bya ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:1175: bdag mdun tha dad du sgrub pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1176: tha mi dad du sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK014(pha)005:1178: bdag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa'i bar byas nas /
NK014(pha)005:1179: de'i nyer bsdu'i n+aa da shin tu phra ba'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK014(pha)005:1180: mdun bskyed la ltos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin mtshams sbyar nas /
NK014(pha)005:1181: slar yang mdun bskyed bsgrub par mdzad mod /
NK014(pha)005:1182: 'di'i gzhung du gsal bar ma bshad kyang /
NK014(pha)005:1183: don gyi dgongs pa lugs phyi ma ltar gnas pas 'dir de ltar bya ste /
NK014(pha)005:1184: de las bsgrub gzhi bdag dang /
NK014(pha)005:1185: bris pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis sgrub chos ting nge 'dzin gsum nas /
NK014(pha)005:1187: zhes pa'i bar gyis gdod nas dag cing grub pa'i
NK014(pha)005:1188: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bdag mdun dbyer med du
NK014(pha)005:1189: gsal btab la / snyan gsan dbab pa /
NK014(pha)005:1191: rig pa'i me tog dor ba /
NK014(pha)005:1192: dngos grub bskul te bstim pa rnams sgrub thabs bzhin shes par bya ba las /
NK014(pha)005:1193: dkyil 'khor rab gnas sogs dang ma 'brel ba'i sgrub
NK014(pha)005:1194: mchod phal pa tsam la sngar nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i
NK014(pha)005:1195: sta gon gyi dkyil 'khor kyang spyan drangs nas skabs
NK014(pha)005:1196: 'dir bstim pa ni khyad par ro //
NK014(pha)005:1197: gsum pa mchod bstod sogs bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:1198: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo las mar me
NK014(pha)005:1199: gcig las gnyis chad ltar gyes pas phyag mchod nas
NK014(pha)005:1200: bzung / dam baca'i mthar thug gi bar sgrub thabs bzhin byas la /
NK014(pha)005:1201: bdag nyid mdun bskyed dang ro gcig tu gyur par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:1202: bzhi pa dzapa bzla ba la /
NK014(pha)005:1203: sa bcad kyi tshangs sgrub thabs bzhin las /
NK014(pha)005:1205: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las /
NK014(pha)005:1206: b+h+r+aum bi shwa sogs kyis bdag dam tshig gi 'khor
NK014(pha)005:1207: lo las mdun bskyed ye shes kyi 'khor lo'i ngo
NK014(pha)005:1208: bor rten dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye
NK014(pha)005:1209: nas / mdun gyi nam mkhar me ri 'dabs 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par mos pa tsam ste /
NK014(pha)005:1210: dmigs pa'i rnam pa sgrub thabs dang dbye ba med kyang /
NK014(pha)005:1211: don gyi ngo bo mi 'dra ba'i gnad shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:1212: dzapa bzla ba na dam ye 'phro 'du ste gsal
NK014(pha)005:1213: ba gsum gyi ngang nas lha so so'i sgos 'dzab
NK014(pha)005:1214: dang gtso bor spyir 'dzab la sgril nas bzla zhing
NK014(pha)005:1215: / so so'i sgos 'dzab bzla ba'i tshe spro na
NK014(pha)005:1216: rang rang gi 'dzab bskul kyang sbyor te gzhan las
NK014(pha)005:1218: gang ltar yang rim bzhin gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar nas ci nus su bzla zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1219: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba'i las rim rnam pa gsum yang sgrub thabs bzhin no //
NK014(pha)005:1220: de dag gi sgrub cing mchod pa'i cho ga'o //
NK014(pha)005:1221: drug pa dbang bskur ba la /
NK014(pha)005:1223: slob ma la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK014(pha)005:1225: slob ma 'jug pa ji lta ba bzhin du dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dbang blang ba'am /
NK014(pha)005:1226: rig pa'i me tog dor ba nyid kyis kyang 'di'i dgos pa 'grub cing /
NK014(pha)005:1227: gang gi tshe yang slob ma 'jug par gnang ba nod pa rnams so //
NK014(pha)005:1228: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug cing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK014(pha)005:1229: dbang gi cho ga zur du 'chad pa las shes par bya'o //
NK014(pha)005:1230: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la lnga las /
NK014(pha)005:1232: gnyis pa brtan skyong ni sgrub thabs kyi dkyus bzhin dang /
NK014(pha)005:1234: gtang rag gi mchod pa bshams la byin gyis brlabs te /
NK014(pha)005:1240: bstod pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs pas bstod /
NK014(pha)005:1242: bzod gsol rnams spyii dang mthun par byas la /
NK014(pha)005:1243: ras bris yin na ye shes pa brtan bzhugs dang /
NK014(pha)005:1244: b+h+r+aum bi shwa sogs kyis dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gsal btab la /
NK014(pha)005:1245: h+aum zhes brjod pas rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyi
NK014(pha)005:1246: phog pas dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas
NK014(pha)005:1247: khang la thim / zhes sogs brjod cing dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsdus la /
NK014(pha)005:1249: lus bsrung sogs mtha' rgyas rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1250: rdul tshon gyi cho ga zhag sbrel mar byed pa'i nyi ma snga ma rnams la'ang de bzhin no //
NK014(pha)005:1251: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gshegs gsol byed na /
NK014(pha)005:1253: zhes pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo nam mkhar btegs nas /
NK014(pha)005:1254: gtang rag gi mchod bstod dang /
NK014(pha)005:1255: bzod gsol sngar bzhin byas la //
NK014(pha)005:1256: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK014(pha)005:1257: sogs kyi mthar dz+ny+aa na man+da la badz+ra muhzhesa gshegs su gsol la /
NK014(pha)005:1258: dam tshig gi 'khor lo sngar bzhin bsdus nas /
NK014(pha)005:1259: go cha bgo zhing lus bsrung ba byas la /
NK014(pha)005:1260: chos thams cad stong pa nyid du mos te /
NK014(pha)005:1261: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas a k+aa ro bzla zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1262: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i lag gis thog mar lha mtshan rnams bsdus la /
NK014(pha)005:1263: cung zad tsam mgo bor bkod /
NK014(pha)005:1264: lhag ma rnams dbang ldan nas brtsams te gtso bo'i
NK014(pha)005:1265: gnas kyi bar du phyags la bum pa la sogs
NK014(pha)005:1266: pa'i snod bzang por blugs nas mchod pa dang bkur
NK014(pha)005:1267: sti chen pos chu klung du dor /
NK014(pha)005:1268: slar yang snod de nyid chus bkang nas nang du
NK014(pha)005:1269: 'ongs te dkyil 'khor khang pa rnams bsang gtor byas
NK014(pha)005:1270: / de nas h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya las mdzub
NK014(pha)005:1271: mo gnyis bsnol ba skam pa'i rgyas 'og gi phur
NK014(pha)005:1272: bu nas bzung mas rim gyis phyungs la /
NK014(pha)005:1273: spyan ma'i sngags bzlas pa'i 'o mas phur rtse bkru zhing /
NK014(pha)005:1274: khung bu rnams la'ang gtor bas bgegs rnams bde stong gi ngo bor sangs rgyas par bsam mo //
NK014(pha)005:1275: de nas dge ba bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa dang /
NK014(pha)005:1276: bkra shis brjod cing dga' ston bya ba la sogs
NK014(pha)005:1277: te rjes kyi bya ba rnams gsang ba spyi'i 'gros
NK014(pha)005:1279: spyi don gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK014(pha)005:1281: des grub pa'i tshad bstan pa ste /
NK014(pha)005:1282: sgrub thabs su bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK014(pha)005:1283: rgyas par gzhan du'ang 'chad par 'dod do //
NK014(pha)005:1284: dpal ldan sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khrag 'thung gi //
NK014(pha)005:1285: snying po'i dkyil 'khor thar pa'i grong khyer du //
NK014(pha)005:1286: myur bder 'jug pa'i thabs tshul bla na med //
NK014(pha)005:1287: dkyil 'khor cho ga'i las kyi rim pa nyid //
NK014(pha)005:1288: de'i phyir rgyud gzhung zab don dgongs pa'i gnad //
NK014(pha)005:1289: grub pa mchog gi phyag bzhes ji lta bar //
NK014(pha)005:1290: ma 'dres gsal bar 'char ba'i ngo mtshar ni //
NK014(pha)005:1291: rdo rje'i phreng ba mchog gis mtshon par byas //
NK014(pha)005:1292: 'di las bsod nams tshogs su gang gyur de //
NK014(pha)005:1293: mkha' mnyam 'gro kun lnga bcu rtsa brgyad lha'i //
NK014(pha)005:1294: bdag po thugs kyi rdo rje dpal chen po'i //
NK014(pha)005:1295: go 'phang bde chen mchog la spyod gyur cig /
NK014(pha)005:1296: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho
NK014(pha)005:1297: ga rdo rje'i phreng ba zhes bya ba 'di yang
NK014(pha)005:1298: rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med rdo rjes sngar bkod
NK014(pha)005:1299: pa'i zhi ba'i dkyil chog nyid gzhir byas /
NK014(pha)005:1300: de las cho ga'i khyad par bye brag pa rnams
NK014(pha)005:1301: tshang zhing gsal la 'jug pa bde bar byas pa
NK014(pha)005:1302: las / thog ma'i yi ger spel ba po ni /
NK014(pha)005:1303: gzhung lugs rab 'byams la mchog tu zab pa'i blo mthun can mkhan chen lo ts+aa ba d+harma sh+r+ai'o //
NK014(pha)005:1305: // lnga bcu rtsa brgyad khrag 'thung dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK014(pha)005:1306: cho ga'i sa bon gcig las grangs med du //
NK014(pha)005:1307: 'phel ba'i spar gyi ljon shing smin grol gling //
